{"bill": {"#text": "\n\t", "form": {"current-chamber": {"#tail": "\n\t\t", "#text": "IN THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES"}, "#text": "\n\t\t", "congress": {"#tail": "\n\t\t", "#text": "113th CONGRESS"}, "#tail": "\n\t", "legis-num": {"#tail": "\n\t\t", "#text": "H. R. 4078"}, "official-title": {"#tail": "\n\t", "#text": "To amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to require that ITIN applicants submit their application\n\t\t\t in person at taxpayer assistance centers, and for other purposes."}, "session": {"#tail": "\n\t\t", "#text": "2d Session"}, "distribution-code": {"#tail": "\n\t\t", "@display": "yes", "#text": "I"}, "action": {"action-date": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t", "@date": "20140225", "#text": "February 25, 2014"}, "#tail": "\n\t\t", "action-desc": {"#tail": "\n\t\t", "#text": "\n        ", "sponsor": {"#tail": " introduced the following bill; which was referred to the ", "#text": "Mr. Sam Johnson of Texas", "@name-id": "J000174"}, "committee-name": {"#tail": "\n      ", "@committee-id": "HWM00", "#text": "Committee on Ways and Means"}}, "#text": "\n\t\t\t"}, "legis-type": {"#tail": "\n\t\t", "#text": "A BILL"}}, "@bill-stage": "Introduced-in-House", "@bill-type": "olc", "@dms-id": "H63F1B5F42033456183C3F4EFE4035ED7", "@public-private": "public", "legis-body": {"#tail": "\n", "@style": "OLC", "section": [{"@section-type": "section-one", "#tail": "\n    ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t", "quote": {"short-title": {"#tail": "\n        ", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": "\n          ", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "ITIN Reform Act of 2014", "@value": "ITIN Reform Act of 2014", "@proposed": "true"}, "#text": "\n            "}, "#tail": ".", "#text": "\n          "}, "#text": "This Act may be cited as the ", "@display-inline": "no-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n      ", "#text": "1."}, "header": {"#tail": "\n      ", "#text": "Short title"}, "#text": "\n      ", "@id": "HE149021FDA844A5D8219B793FBC9393B"}, {"@section-type": "subsequent-section", "#tail": "\n  ", "enum": {"#tail": "\n      ", "#text": "2."}, "header": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t", "#text": "Requirements for the issuance of ITINs"}, "subsection": [{"#tail": "\n      ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": " is amended by adding at the end the following:", "@entity-type": "uscode", "#text": "\n            ", "external-xref": {"#tail": " of the Internal Revenue Code of 1986", "@parsable-cite": "usc/26/6109", "#text": "Section 6109", "@legal-doc": "usc"}, "@value": "usc/26/6109"}, "#text": "\n          ", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "(a)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "In general"}, "quoted-block": {"@style": "OLC", "after-quoted-block": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "."}, "#tail": "\n\t\t\t", "subsection": {"#tail": "\n          ", "enum": {"#tail": "\n            ", "#text": "(i)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "Special rules relating to the issuance of ITINs"}, "paragraph": [{"#tail": "\n            ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": " and ", "@entity-type": "uscode", "#text": "paragraphs (2)", "@value": "usc/26/6109/i/2", "@proposed": "true"}, {"#tail": " are met.", "@entity-type": "uscode", "#text": "(3)", "@value": "usc/26/6109/i/3", "@proposed": "true"}], "#text": "The Secretary may issue an individual taxpayer identification number to an individual only if the\n\t\t\t requirements of "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "(1)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "In general"}, "#text": "\n              ", "@id": "HB15C15A2FB3E44DC8D73A73970DBF8D8"}, {"#tail": "\n            ", "@id": "HDA4F712AAF704CCFB3A55598EFD374F7", "enum": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "(2)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "In-person application"}, "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "The requirements of this paragraph are met if, with respect to an application for an individual\n\t\t\t taxpayer identification number\u2014"}, "#text": "\n              ", "subparagraph": [{"#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": ", or", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Internal Revenue Service", "@entity-id": "2050"}, "#text": "the applicant submits an application in person, using Form W\u20137 (or any successor thereof) and\n\t\t\t including the required documentation, at a taxpayer assistance center of\n\t\t\t the "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(A)"}, "@id": "H9D21D6E0C3C74C69AE203F2688384070", "#text": "\n                "}, {"#tail": "\n            ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": " or a\n\t\t\t designee of the Secretary at a United States diplomatic mission or\n\t\t\t consular post, together with the required documentation.", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Internal Revenue Service", "@entity-id": "2050"}, "#text": "in the case of an applicant who resides outside of the United States, the applicant submits the\n\t\t\t application in person to an employee of the ", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(B)"}, "@id": "HDB1B25B5F07F4439B9ABEE4167A1C22E", "#text": "\n                "}]}, {"#tail": "\n            ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": " at the taxpayer assistance center, or the\n\t\t\t employee or designee described in ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Internal Revenue Service", "@entity-id": "2050"}, {"#tail": ", as the case may be,\n\t\t\t conducts an initial verification of the documentation supporting the\n\t\t\t application submitted under ", "@entity-type": "uscode", "#text": "paragraph (2)(B)", "@value": "usc/26/6109/i/2/B", "@proposed": "true"}, {"#tail": ".", "@entity-type": "uscode", "#text": "paragraph (2)", "@value": "usc/26/6109/i/2", "@proposed": "true"}], "#text": "The requirements of this paragraph are met if, with respect to each application, an employee of the\n\t\t\t "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "(3)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "Initial on-site verification of documentation"}, "#text": "\n              ", "@id": "H4C60573B087B4C83ABC7B50BA6656052"}, {"#tail": "\n            ", "@id": "H2C7D51F0B22D4BE299A6E113CFE3A748", "enum": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "(4)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "Required documentation"}, "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "For purposes of this subsection\u2014", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "#text": "\n              ", "subparagraph": [{"#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": " may require that proves the\n\t\t\t individual\u2019s identity and foreign status, and", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Secretary", "@entity-id": "2000"}, "#text": "required documentation includes such documentation as the "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(A)"}, "@id": "H4210687B219543C6BA0CC3D40460FEA8", "#text": "\n                "}, {"#tail": "\n            ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "the Secretary may only accept original documents."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(B)"}, "@id": "HBD843E9DB2374952A48FA53F490F4E2B", "#text": "\n                "}]}, {"#tail": "\n            ", "subparagraph": [{"#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": " shall not apply to the spouse, or the dependents, without a social security number of\n\t\t\t a taxpayer who is a member of the Armed Forces of the United States.", "@entity-type": "uscode", "#text": "Paragraph (1)", "@value": "usc/26/6109/i/1", "@proposed": "true"}, "#text": "\n                  ", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(A)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "Military spouses"}, "#text": "\n                ", "@id": "HC98ECBA348974268A1A5B3F7232E38C4"}, {"#tail": "\n            ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": " shall not apply to a nonresident alien applying for an individual taxpayer\n\t\t\t identification number for the purpose of claiming tax treaty benefits.", "@entity-type": "uscode", "#text": "Paragraph (1)", "@value": "usc/26/6109/i/1", "@proposed": "true"}, "#text": "\n                  "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(B)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "Treaty benefits"}, "#text": "\n                ", "@id": "H61111005A3C84A83BD33FEA5B35D1CCF"}], "enum": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "(5)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "Exceptions"}, "#text": "\n              ", "@id": "HDA72D3572D73450A9A6529110F323F45"}, {"#tail": "\n          ", "subparagraph": [{"#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "An individual taxpayer identification number issued after the date of the enactment of this\n\t\t\t subsection shall be valid only for the 5-year period which includes the\n\t\t\t taxable year of the individual for which such number is issued and the 4\n\t\t\t succeeding taxable years."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(A)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "In general"}, "#text": "\n                ", "@id": "HB2899F30AA084F1CB2B8AA43E91A67D3"}, {"#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": " and ", "@entity-type": "uscode", "#text": "paragraphs (2)", "@value": "usc/26/6109/i/2", "@proposed": "true"}, {"#tail": ".", "@entity-type": "uscode", "#text": "(3)", "@value": "usc/26/6109/i/3", "@proposed": "true"}], "#text": "Such number shall be valid for an additional 5-year period only if it is renewed through an\n\t\t\t application which satisfies the requirements under "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(B)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "Renewal of ITIN"}, "#text": "\n                ", "@id": "H95352F7700774994857314FEC6BAEB41"}, {"#tail": "\n            ", "clause": [{"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "the end of the 3-year period beginning on the date of the enactment of this subsection, or"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(i)"}, "@id": "H9E6F8A636A5C43BB8CE4627F4BE84C0F", "#text": "\n                  "}, {"#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "the first taxable year beginning after\u2014"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(ii)"}, "subclause": [{"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "the date of the enactment of this subsection, and"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(I)"}, "@id": "HDE8E0FAE1F0948C1AA50E03E072A459D", "#text": "\n                    "}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "any taxable year for which the individual (or, if a dependent, on which the individual is included)\n\t\t\t did not make a return."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(II)"}, "@id": "H2189B689E2B04D23985328E95D4F212A", "#text": "\n                    "}], "#text": "\n                  ", "@id": "HA967E18C9CBA4BE9B242280719CB3806"}], "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(C)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "Special rule for existing ITINs"}, "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "In the case of an individual with an individual taxpayer identification number issued on or before\n\t\t\t the date of the enactment of this subsection, such number shall not be\n\t\t\t valid after the earlier of\u2014"}, "#text": "\n                ", "@id": "H0B09223C2DD44194AF49AC9962764EB3"}], "enum": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "(6)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "Term"}, "#text": "\n              ", "@id": "H2FE22DDDB53F4AC3B709EF12E24786E1"}], "#text": "\n            ", "@id": "HC873FC8C53BA4FF683C48D75A70DEDDC"}, "@display-inline": "no-display-inline", "#text": "\n\t\t\t\t\t", "@id": "HC5F838EC3E6445DB8C770D8A4C55C455"}, "#text": "\n        ", "@id": "HDA428AEE74094A36B6266EE75498ABD3"}, {"#tail": "\n      ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": " is amended by redesignating ", "@entity-type": "uscode", "#text": "Section 6611 of such Code", "@value": "usc/26/6611"}, {"#tail": " as ", "@entity-type": "uscode", "#text": "subsection (h)", "@value": "usc/26/6611/h"}, {"#tail": " and by\n\t\t\t inserting after ", "@entity-type": "uscode", "#text": "subsection (i)", "@value": "usc/26/6611/i", "@proposed": "true"}, {"#tail": " the following new subsection:", "@entity-type": "uscode", "#text": "subsection (g)", "@value": "usc/26/6611/g"}], "#text": "\n          "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "(b)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "Interest"}, "quoted-block": {"@style": "OLC", "after-quoted-block": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "."}, "#tail": "\n\t\t\t", "subsection": {"#tail": "\n          ", "text": {"#tail": "\n          ", "#text": "Notwithstanding any other provision of this section, no interest shall be allowed or paid to or on\n\t\t\t behalf of an individual with respect to any overpayment until 45 days\n\t\t\t after\n\t\t\t an individual taxpayer identification number is issued to the individual.", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n            ", "#text": "(h)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n            ", "#text": "Special rule relating to ITINs"}, "#text": "\n            ", "@id": "H8C503C9349184CA3B67EE37E41A83C50"}, "@display-inline": "no-display-inline", "#text": "\n\t\t\t\t\t", "@id": "H4C46611AC9924A57B85434C84672FD87"}, "#text": "\n        ", "@id": "HD2BFC0A7E9534C16ADFD3ECDDEEA2818"}, {"#tail": "\n      ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": " shall\n\t\t\t conduct an audit of the program of the ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Treasury Inspector General for Tax Administration", "@entity-id": "2014"}, {"#tail": " for the\n\t\t\t issuance of individual taxpayer identification numbers pursuant to ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Internal Revenue Service", "@entity-id": "2050"}, {"#tail": ". The report required by this\n\t\t\t subsection shall be submitted to the ", "@entity-type": "uscode", "#text": "section\n\t\t\t 6109(i) of the Internal Revenue Code of 1986", "@value": "usc/26/6109/i"}, {"#tail": ".", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Congress", "@entity-id": "0001"}], "#text": "Not later than two years after the date of the enactment of this Act, and every two years\n\t\t\t thereafter, the "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "(c)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "Audit by TIGTA"}, "#text": "\n        ", "@id": "HF3839DD78AB549BC9DD098784A473F2F"}, {"#tail": "\n    ", "enum": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "(d)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t", "#text": "Effective date"}, "paragraph": [{"#tail": "\n        ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": " shall apply to requests for individual taxpayer identification\n\t\t\t numbers made after the date of the enactment of this Act.", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "subsection (a)", "@value": "ITIN Reform Act of 2014/s:2/ss:a", "@proposed": "true"}, "#text": "The amendment made by "}, "enu